OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny evening
OL,6,Fshowers fading to leave a dry night,
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fclear spells. Perhaps a few mist and
OL,9,Ffog patches forming by dawn. Locally
OL,10,Fchilly. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEarly mist and fog patches
OL,13,Fsoon clearing to give a cloudy and
OL,14,Fmostly dry day. Some brighter spells
OL,15,Fat times, with the odd light afternoon
OL,16,Fshower possible. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
