OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain clearing to give mostly
OL,7,Ffine and dry conditions Thursday.
OL,8,FFeeling cooler. Becoming unsettled
OL,9,Fwith some rain at times Friday and
OL,10,FSaturday. Often windy and relatively
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
